full_title_(бүтэн_гарчиг): *, ,MI SKAR MI CHEN LNGA PO'I BSANGS GSER SKYEMS BZHUGS SO, ,
colophon_(төгсгөлийн_үг): @003A *, ,(CES MI SKAR MI CHEN LNGA POS LA BSANGS MCHOD BZA' BTUNG SOGS 'BRU SNA MDOR BSDUS PHAN YON BSAM GYI MI KHYAB PAS BSAM KUN SGRUB ZHES BYA GNYIS 'DI NI MI SKAR MI CHEN LNGA PO LA BSANGS MCHOD 'PHUL BA LA SNA TSOGS GANG BSAM LA MYUR DU SGRUB PA YIS, ,'DI NI SNGON KHA MAN NGAG YIN, ,SKAR MI MI YI THAMS CAD DBANG BSDUS LA MI NANG PHYUGS NAD GOD KHA ZHI BA DANG, NAD RIMS TAL YAMS BAR CHAD SEL, ,'THAB RTZOD 'KHRUGS LONG MI KHA KHA MCHU BRAM MCHU SOGS GZHAN GYI MI THUB PA 'GAL RKYEN SEL ZHING MTHUN RKYEN 'GRUB, ,TSE DANG BSOD NAMS DPAL 'BYOR SNYAN GRAGS LONGS SPYOD 'PHEL, ,THE TSOM MED CING NGES PAR ZAB CING 'DI NI CHA HAR DGE BA'I  BSHES GNYEN BZHIN DU SBYAR BA'O, ,MANGGA LAm, ,)
